			play them once (click on the §talkingHead§ icon) or several times (§infinity§ icon).
		</Hm802>
		<Hm803>If it&apos;s useful you can reduce the playback speed (vertical slider).</Hm803>
		<Hm804>Try to repeat what you hear</Hm804> 
